The use of regret minimization is a common technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG), and the paper explicitly mentions regret minimization as a key component of their analysis. The VCG mechanism is a well-known mechanism in economics and mechanism design (cs.EC). Finally, the paper uses mathematical analysis to prove the performance of the VCG mechanism, which suggests a focus on algorithms and complexity (cs.DS).
